description: (716) Club House is winning over the hungry folks of Western New York with their champion selection of hearty club sandwiches. This big bold truck is taking Buffalo’s favorite bar fare to everyone within the (716) area. Local ingredients are used to craft their delicious menu that  includes the Chicken Nacho Hoagie (with tender marinated chicken, house-made salsa, and topped with jalapeno cheese sauce, banana peppers, and crunchy corn tortilla chips), the Clubhouse Double Melt (half club/half grilled cheese sandwich with melted gouda and grilled mozzarella with Sahlen’s smoked turkey and applewood bacon), and the Fried Bologna Helicopter (thick-cut bologna topped with caramelized onion, applewood bacon, Great Lakes American Cheese, Webers Mustard, all heaped on a Costanzo Kaiser Roll), and many more!If you’re craving tasty sandwiches, join the club, and get yourself over to this awesome truck!
name: (716) Club House
